{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/posts/pgi3sie52rrgrzh9/","result":{"data":{"sitePage":null},"pageContext":{"url":"posts/pgi3sie52rrgrzh9","relativePath":"posts/pgi3sie52rrgrzh9","frontmatter":{"title":"【已解决】CryptographicException: The key  was not found in the key ring 以及 Unable to unprotect the message.State 错误","stackbit_url_path":"posts/pgi3sie52rrgrzh9","date":"2023-01-11T04:08:30","excerpt":"","tags":[],"categories":[],"template":"post"},"html":"<p><a name=JyyN6></a></p>\n<h1>问题</h1>\n<p>最早我部署了一个 IdentityServer 到 Azure （《<a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/580160351\">身份验证哪家强？IdentityServer 初体验 - Jeff Tian的文章 - 知乎)(https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/482103322) 》），一切顺利。但是，本着狡兔三窟的自由架构原则（《(Free Arch: 狡兔三窟，多处部署 - Jeff Tian的文章 - 知乎</a> 》），我又将它部署到了 Okteto（《<a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/591856146\">Free Arch： 将 IdentityServer 部署到 Okteto - Jeff Tian的文章 - 知乎</a>  》）。本来也是一切顺利，直到我将它的 replica 设置成了 2，就登录不了了！\nshell\nkubectl autoscale deployment/id6 --min=2 --max=2</p>\n<p>也就是说，如果将 K8S 环境里的 IdentityServer 应用，启动多个副本，就不能正常工作了！报的错误是：\nshell\nCryptographicException: The key {9bfdfefa-e156-457e-975f-56b3118dd6e1} was not found in the key ring. For more information go to <a href=\"http://aka.ms/dataprotectionwarning\">http://aka.ms/dataprotectionwarning</a></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4dfc70bdea24e7d39bd124f358660261/0907e/1673260788145-326e198a-7278-4955-bdba-42d577b4b925.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.37837837837838%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image.png\"\n        title=\"image.png\"\n        src=\"/static/4dfc70bdea24e7d39bd124f358660261/fcda8/1673260788145-326e198a-7278-4955-bdba-42d577b4b925.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4dfc70bdea24e7d39bd124f358660261/12f09/1673260788145-326e198a-7278-4955-bdba-42d577b4b925.png 148w,\n/static/4dfc70bdea24e7d39bd124f358660261/e4a3f/1673260788145-326e198a-7278-4955-bdba-42d577b4b925.png 295w,\n/static/4dfc70bdea24e7d39bd124f358660261/fcda8/1673260788145-326e198a-7278-4955-bdba-42d577b4b925.png 590w,\n/static/4dfc70bdea24e7d39bd124f358660261/efc66/1673260788145-326e198a-7278-4955-bdba-42d577b4b925.png 885w,\n/static/4dfc70bdea24e7d39bd124f358660261/c83ae/1673260788145-326e198a-7278-4955-bdba-42d577b4b925.png 1180w,\n/static/4dfc70bdea24e7d39bd124f358660261/0907e/1673260788145-326e198a-7278-4955-bdba-42d577b4b925.png 3788w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><a name=XOZm1></a></p>\n<h1>分析</h1>\n<p>看起来，在登录过程中，它需要做一些数据查询工作，当只有一个副本时，一切正常，而多个副本时，出现了问题，于是我推断这是由于在登录过程中涉及多个请求及一些跳转，导致第一个请求和第二个请求打在了不同的 pod。而第一个请求会让服务器端设置一些数据（状态）到当前的 pod 内存中，另一个 pod 并不能查询到。</p>\n<p>要解决这个问题，方向应该是将这个状态存储从应用本身移到外部的存储。\n<a name=yp7cK></a></p>\n<h1>排查</h1>\n<p>通过查看一些文档，发现这个 Microsoft.AspNetCore.DataProtection 问题并不是 IdentityServer 本身独有的，而是 ASP.NET core 应用都会遇到的。相关的文档链接是： <a href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/aspnet/core/security/data-protection/implementation/key-storage-providers?view=aspnetcore-7.0&#x26;tabs=visual-studio\">https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/aspnet/core/security/data-protection/implementation/key-storage-providers?view=aspnetcore-7.0&#x26;tabs=visual-studio</a>。文档中列举了多种外部存储：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>文件系统</li>\n<li>Azure Storage</li>\n<li>Redis</li>\n<li>注册中心（只适用于 Windows 部署）</li>\n<li>Entity Framework Core</li>\n<li>自定义的 key 仓库</li>\n</ul>\n<p>由于我部署的 IdentityServer 已经使用了 Postgres 数据库，后面也将使用 Entity Framework Core 来做更多的数据存储，因此我倾向于先用 Entity Framework Core 方案，文档中也给了相关的关键代码示例，我还在 GitHub 上找到了一个完整的使用 Entity Framework Core 来存储 DataProtection 相关数据的示例： <a href=\"https://github.com/dotnet/aspnetcore/blob/v3.1.4/src/DataProtection/samples/EntityFrameworkCoreSample/Program.cs\">https://github.com/dotnet/aspnetcore/blob/v3.1.4/src/DataProtection/samples/EntityFrameworkCoreSample/Program.cs</a> 。</p>\n<p><a name=GVEd4></a></p>\n<h1>解决 CryptographicException</h1>\n<p>解决 DataProtection 问题的提交，详见： <a href=\"https://github.com/Jeff-Tian/IdentityServer/commit/ea750e484cfd1ade371fafdb2ebe8f923ecc10e8\">https://github.com/Jeff-Tian/IdentityServer/commit/ea750e484cfd1ade371fafdb2ebe8f923ecc10e8</a> 。\n<a name=LsxFI></a></p>\n<h2>第一步，添加引用</h2>\n<p>xml\n<PackageReference Include=Microsoft.AspNetCore.DataProtection.EntityFrameworkCore Version=6.0.0 /></p>\n<p><a name=Ysqwl></a></p>\n<h2>第二步，添加 DataProtectionKeys 的 DbContext</h2>\n<p>csharp\nusing Microsoft.AspNetCore.DataProtection.EntityFrameworkCore;\nusing Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore;</p>\n<p>namespace DataProtection;</p>\n<p>public class MyKeysContext : DbContext, IDataProtectionKeyContext\n{\npublic MyKeysContext(DbContextOptions<MyKeysContext> options) : base(options)\n{\n}</p>\n<pre><code>public DbSet&#x3C;DataProtectionKey> DataProtectionKeys { get; set; }\n</code></pre>\n<p>}</p>\n<p><a name=Nvxyp></a></p>\n<h2>第三步，添加 Db Migrations</h2>\n<p>shell\ndotnet ef migrations add AddDataProtectionKeys --context MyKeysContext --project hosts/main/Host.Main.csproj\ndotnet ef database update --context MyKeysContext  --project hosts/main/Host.Main.csproj</p>\n<p>这样，项目中就多了几个文件：<br /><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1605df1d0b17c2045c68c1bb062317d9/b6425/1673409008097-4116c457-d888-4552-9457-bb003bb54350.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 86.48648648648648%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image.png\"\n        title=\"image.png\"\n        src=\"/static/1605df1d0b17c2045c68c1bb062317d9/fcda8/1673409008097-4116c457-d888-4552-9457-bb003bb54350.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1605df1d0b17c2045c68c1bb062317d9/12f09/1673409008097-4116c457-d888-4552-9457-bb003bb54350.png 148w,\n/static/1605df1d0b17c2045c68c1bb062317d9/e4a3f/1673409008097-4116c457-d888-4552-9457-bb003bb54350.png 295w,\n/static/1605df1d0b17c2045c68c1bb062317d9/fcda8/1673409008097-4116c457-d888-4552-9457-bb003bb54350.png 590w,\n/static/1605df1d0b17c2045c68c1bb062317d9/efc66/1673409008097-4116c457-d888-4552-9457-bb003bb54350.png 885w,\n/static/1605df1d0b17c2045c68c1bb062317d9/c83ae/1673409008097-4116c457-d888-4552-9457-bb003bb54350.png 1180w,\n/static/1605df1d0b17c2045c68c1bb062317d9/b6425/1673409008097-4116c457-d888-4552-9457-bb003bb54350.png 2336w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><a name=T0Jmq></a></p>\n<h2>第四步，添加 DbContext 以及部署后自动 Migration 的代码</h2>\n<p>csharp\nbuilder.Services.AddDbContext<MyKeysContext>(options => { options.UseNpgsql(connectionString); })\n.AddDataProtection().PersistKeysToDbContext<MyKeysContext>();</p>\n<pre><code>using var scope = webApp.Services.CreateScope();\nConsole.WriteLine(Start migrating databases. Caution! Only run this on non-prod env!);\n\nvar applicationDbContext = scope.ServiceProvider.GetRequiredService&#x3C;MyKeysContext>();\napplicationDbContext.Database.Migrate();\n\nConsole.WriteLine(Migrating done.);\n</code></pre>\n<p><a name=o1462></a></p>\n<h2>第五步，提交代码，等待自动部署完成</h2>\n<p>经过测试，CryptographicException 的错误不存在了，已解决！</p>\n<p><a name=S8oQk></a></p>\n<h1>好事多磨，新的错误出现了</h1>\n<p>以上 CryptographicException 的错误消失后，在使用 Azure AD 登录的前几步，顺利通过了，但是在回调回来后，又出现了新的错误：<strong>Unable to unprotect the message.State</strong>。</p>\n<p><a name=NqMNa></a></p>\n<h1>再次排查</h1>\n<p>这一步，搜索了很多相关文章，都在说和 DataProtection 相关的事情，然而这一步我在上面已经做过了。再次将 pod 数改成 1 个，登录正常。改成 2 个，出现 Unable to unprotect the message.State 错误，所以，推测还是有一些数据被缓存在内存中了。</p>\n<p>虽然不知道具体是什么数据，但是我想起来之前在另一个 ASP.NET 项目中，启用过分布式缓存，于是决定往这个方向试一试，还真有效。</p>\n<p><a name=bILQn></a></p>\n<h1>解决 Unable to unprotect the message.State 错误</h1>\n<p>完整提交见： <a href=\"https://github.com/Jeff-Tian/IdentityServer/commit/16995efe103aac8390e87eb72f39d06493c9e378\">https://github.com/Jeff-Tian/IdentityServer/commit/16995efe103aac8390e87eb72f39d06493c9e378</a></p>\n<p><a name=DczNt></a></p>\n<h2>第一步，添加引用</h2>\n<p>因为项目使用了 PostgreSQL，决定继续用 PostgreSQL 来做分布式缓存。这需要引用一个社区包：\nxml\n<PackageReference Include=Community.Microsoft.Extensions.Caching.PostgreSql Version=4.0.2 /></p>\n<p><a name=Dv9rq></a></p>\n<h2>第二步，增加分布式缓存代码</h2>\n<p>csharp\nbuilder.Services.AddDistributedPostgreSqlCache(setup =>\n{\nsetup.ConnectionString = connectionString;\nsetup.SchemaName = public;\nsetup.TableName = distcache;\nsetup.DisableRemoveExpired = true;\nsetup.CreateInfrastructure = true;\nsetup.ExpiredItemsDeletionInterval = TimeSpan.FromMinutes(30);\n});</p>\n<p><a name=xD9Wh></a></p>\n<h2>第三步，提交代码，等待部署完成</h2>\n<p>再次使用 Azure AD 登录，成功返回，并能够获取当前登录用户的信息了：</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/cdaf092eefe40642e910e411634f693e/cdf95/1673409891956-c7fa027c-16f9-4327-aa39-7ff27ec88540.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 43.24324324324324%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image.png\"\n        title=\"image.png\"\n        src=\"/static/cdaf092eefe40642e910e411634f693e/fcda8/1673409891956-c7fa027c-16f9-4327-aa39-7ff27ec88540.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/cdaf092eefe40642e910e411634f693e/12f09/1673409891956-c7fa027c-16f9-4327-aa39-7ff27ec88540.png 148w,\n/static/cdaf092eefe40642e910e411634f693e/e4a3f/1673409891956-c7fa027c-16f9-4327-aa39-7ff27ec88540.png 295w,\n/static/cdaf092eefe40642e910e411634f693e/fcda8/1673409891956-c7fa027c-16f9-4327-aa39-7ff27ec88540.png 590w,\n/static/cdaf092eefe40642e910e411634f693e/efc66/1673409891956-c7fa027c-16f9-4327-aa39-7ff27ec88540.png 885w,\n/static/cdaf092eefe40642e910e411634f693e/c83ae/1673409891956-c7fa027c-16f9-4327-aa39-7ff27ec88540.png 1180w,\n/static/cdaf092eefe40642e910e411634f693e/cdf95/1673409891956-c7fa027c-16f9-4327-aa39-7ff27ec88540.png 2106w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3008714d5738c429431627dc1eed6fbf/a8a6f/1673409920788-2a951236-8635-4ad3-bf18-9d2534c07be4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 22.2972972972973%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image.png\"\n        title=\"image.png\"\n        src=\"/static/3008714d5738c429431627dc1eed6fbf/fcda8/1673409920788-2a951236-8635-4ad3-bf18-9d2534c07be4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3008714d5738c429431627dc1eed6fbf/12f09/1673409920788-2a951236-8635-4ad3-bf18-9d2534c07be4.png 148w,\n/static/3008714d5738c429431627dc1eed6fbf/e4a3f/1673409920788-2a951236-8635-4ad3-bf18-9d2534c07be4.png 295w,\n/static/3008714d5738c429431627dc1eed6fbf/fcda8/1673409920788-2a951236-8635-4ad3-bf18-9d2534c07be4.png 590w,\n/static/3008714d5738c429431627dc1eed6fbf/efc66/1673409920788-2a951236-8635-4ad3-bf18-9d2534c07be4.png 885w,\n/static/3008714d5738c429431627dc1eed6fbf/c83ae/1673409920788-2a951236-8635-4ad3-bf18-9d2534c07be4.png 1180w,\n/static/3008714d5738c429431627dc1eed6fbf/a8a6f/1673409920788-2a951236-8635-4ad3-bf18-9d2534c07be4.png 1516w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><a name=hthc4></a></p>\n<h1>未完待续</h1>\n<p>本来，这两个错误解决后，以为万事大吉。然而，事情还没有完。现在虽然能够正常登录了，但是发现，无论点击哪个登录页面，都会展示要求登录后才能查看（注意上图中的 url，就是被登录拦截了呢）。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9c745c3a38445240a0eb287f8f87effd/2b984/1673410046036-5c9bbed5-0a4a-4157-9639-cb70e8e98910.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 69.5945945945946%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image.png\"\n        title=\"image.png\"\n        src=\"/static/9c745c3a38445240a0eb287f8f87effd/fcda8/1673410046036-5c9bbed5-0a4a-4157-9639-cb70e8e98910.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9c745c3a38445240a0eb287f8f87effd/12f09/1673410046036-5c9bbed5-0a4a-4157-9639-cb70e8e98910.png 148w,\n/static/9c745c3a38445240a0eb287f8f87effd/e4a3f/1673410046036-5c9bbed5-0a4a-4157-9639-cb70e8e98910.png 295w,\n/static/9c745c3a38445240a0eb287f8f87effd/fcda8/1673410046036-5c9bbed5-0a4a-4157-9639-cb70e8e98910.png 590w,\n/static/9c745c3a38445240a0eb287f8f87effd/efc66/1673410046036-5c9bbed5-0a4a-4157-9639-cb70e8e98910.png 885w,\n/static/9c745c3a38445240a0eb287f8f87effd/c83ae/1673410046036-5c9bbed5-0a4a-4157-9639-cb70e8e98910.png 1180w,\n/static/9c745c3a38445240a0eb287f8f87effd/2b984/1673410046036-5c9bbed5-0a4a-4157-9639-cb70e8e98910.png 2164w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>也就是说，页面的不同部分，对登录状态的感知不同。看起来还没有完全消除这个状态数据共享的问题。今天太累了，就到这里，下次再继续研究并分享解决方案。</p>","pages":[],"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Jeff Tian","author":"@zizhujy","description":"A wild full stack developer","pa